data.description: This 5-bedroom turn-of-the century farmhouse has a newly updated kitchen, formal dining room, and much of the original charm it was built with. Wood floors on the first and second floors, large pantry, detached two car garage with chicken coop, 8-person hot tub, and a large, private yard make this property even more appealing. The attached barn has been completely remodeled to include 5 10x10 growing rooms, a dry room, and additional finished attic grow space above if someone wanted to start a business.  Mere blocks from Main Street, 15 minutes from Farmington, less than an hour from Sugarloaf/Saddleback and access to ATV trails nearby make accessing the area's recreational activities very simple.
